CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 6, 1946, pg. 25, reads: "YMCA Tournament Champions - ... Right: The classy 'Y' Rens, who won the Intermediate Championship. The Rens include Teenie Harris Jr., Leonard Harley, Henry Payne, Jesse Bell, Tummy Malden [Tunnie Moulden], Fowler Johnson, Hanny Thompson, Eddie Ellis, Billy Crandall and Lonnie Mitchell. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Pittsburgh Y Rens basketball team including #6 Charles A. "Little Teenie" Harris, #11 Leonard Harley, #10 Henry Payne, #13 Jesse Bell, #9 Tunnie Moulden, #8 Fowler Johnson, #7 Henry "Honey Boy" Thompson, coach Eddie Ellis, #5 Billy Crandall, and #0 Lonnie Mitchell, posed with YMCA Intermediate Championship trophy, in gymnasium
